Interface MyList<T>


  • public interface MyList<T>
    ADT MyList: Public Part
    . The interface includes all the operations available to a MyList user

      void addElement(int index, T item)
      Given a concrete MyList, an index and an item, it adds the item at the desired index of MyList (if capacity allows it).

      Given a concrete MyList and a concrete index, it returns the item placed at that index (if any).

      Given a concrete MyList, it returns its number of items.
